item.title: 🎤 Giving your first conference talk 💡✨
item.description:
So you’ve hit submit on that talk proposal and—surprise!—an email lands in your inbox: your talk has been accepted 🎉💌. First of all, congratulations! That’s a huge achievement. Now the fun (and slightly scary) part begins: preparing for your very first conference talk.

⚠️ Disclaimer: My experience was with an AWS event, so every conference may run a little differently. But I hope these tips will still help you feel more confident and ready. 💪
